dcterms:description: The Citeseer dataset is a citation network of scientific publications, where each node represents a publication and edges represent citation relationships. The dataset contains 3,327 nodes, 4,732 edges, and 3,703 features, with publications classified into six domains.
dcterms:title: Citeseer

dcterms:description: The PubMed dataset is a citation network of scientific publications, where each node represents a publication and edges represent citation relationships. It contains 19,717 nodes, 44,338 edges, and 500 features, with publications classified into three categories related to diabetes.
